headline: CBRE Group Stock Gains 17.6% in 6 Months: Will it Continue to Rise?
summary: CBRE shares are up 17.4% in six months, lifted by resilient outsourcing demand, acquisitions, and tech investments supporting growth.

headline: CBRE Group, Inc. Announces Details of Conference Call and Webcast for Fourth Quarter and Full-Year 2025 Financial Results
summary: DALLAS, January 12, 2026--CBRE Group, Inc. (NYSE: CBRE) will release its fourth quarter and full-year 2025 financial results at approximately 6:55 a.m. Eastern time on Thursday, February 12, 2026. Management will hold a conference call to discuss these results at 8:30 a.m. Eastern time on that same day (Thursday, February 12, 2026).
